</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Ponds" /><category term="Flowers" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Cosmos already? These orange flowers at Hirosawa Pond seem like they stay in bloom year round. コスモスはもう咲いているのか？？？広沢池のオレンジ色の花は、一年中咲いているように見える。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2408_A7R04139.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2408_A7R04139.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sunrise Over Arashiyama・嵐山の朝日</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240813/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sunrise Over Arashiyama・嵐山の朝日" /><published>2024-08-13T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-08-13T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/arashiyama-sunrise</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240813/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
