</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Sunrise" /><category term="Katsura River" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The rising sun reflected in the Katsura River, taken from Arashiyama’s Togetsu Bridge. 嵐山の渡月橋から撮影した、桂川に映る昇る太陽。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2408_A7R01818-Pano.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2408_A7R01818-Pano.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Looking Up・見上げる</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240812/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Looking Up・見上げる" /><published>2024-08-12T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-08-12T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kyoto-tower</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240812/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
