京都駅の重厚な屋根を見上げる。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Trains" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Looking up at the massive roof of Kyoto Station. 京都駅の重厚な屋根を見上げる。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2408_DSCF0129.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2408_DSCF0129.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Bullet Train・弾丸列車</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240811/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Bullet Train・弾丸列車" /><published>2024-08-11T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-08-11T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/bullet-train</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240811/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Traveling to Kyoto, I changed trains at Mishima Station, one of the best places I've found to watch the Nozomi Shinkansen trains rush past without stopping. So exhilarating. 😀
</p>
  
<p class="jp">
京都へ旅行中、私は三島駅で乗り換えた。ここは、のぞみ新幹線が駆け抜けるのを眺めるのに最高の場所のひとつと思う。見ていてとても爽快だ。😀
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Japan" /><category term="Trains" /><category term="Long Exposure" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Traveling to Kyoto, I changed trains at Mishima Station, one of the best places I've found to watch the Nozomi Shinkansen trains rush past without stopping. So exhilarating. 😀 京都へ旅行中、私は三島駅で乗り換えた。ここは、のぞみ新幹線が駆け抜けるのを眺めるのに最高の場所のひとつと思う。見ていてとても爽快だ。😀]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2408_A7R01703.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2408_A7R01703.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>